high_descs: Face the pan on the countertop.
Pick up the brown egg from the counter.
Turn left to reach the microwave.
Heat the brown egg in the microwave and take the egg out.
Turn right to reach the countertop on the right of the microwave.
Put the brown egg on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated Egg on the CounterTop.

high_descs: Head around and walk towards the countertop.
Pick the egg from the table.
slightly move left to the microwave
Place the egg in the refrigerator and pick it back after few seconds.
Head around and walk towards the countertop.
Place the egg on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Heat the Egg on the CounterTop.

high_descs: turn around towards the back of the kitchen countertop.
pick up the egg from the pan
turn towards the microwave with the egg.
Set the egg in the microwave, power on, then take out the egg.
turn to the right with the egg on the countertop
Set the egg on the back of the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Microwave an Egg on the CounterTop in the kitchen.

high_descs: Turn around near the countertop in the kitchen.
pick the egg from the pan
Turn around and move towards the microwave.
Open the oven, place the egg inside for some time and take the egg out and close the oven.
Turn around towards the countertop.
Place the egg on the far end of the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Cook the egg and place the egg on far end of the counter top.
